I had to create these custom hair extension’s for @lexypanterra since her natural hair is curly, I got her #naturallycurly 34” #weftextensions In dark brown, natural color. These were the steps:
1- lightly bleach the wefts
2- Color the hair to match her existing color
3- create #keratinbonds out of the #weftextensions 
4- install the individually pre-bonded #KTips 
5- cut the #extensions to blend to her natural hair 

The whole process took a couple of days before she came in and a couple of hours the day she came in to install and blend 💇‍♀️🤪🔥💃💥

This method of application, which is the keratin extensions, when done right is the longest lasting extensions method without any maintenance which last up to six months. These K tip extensions were converted from  #weftextensions Kylie 🤍 had when she first came in.

 since we didn’t want to waste the hair we ended up converting them into #keratinhairextensions  #KTips. 

My client never had a #ktipextensions She only had Wefts and she wasn’t sure about changing but once we finished, she was so happy that she made the change. 

KTips are so much more comfortable than the #wefts extensions, besides being able to do a lot more with your hair in terms of styling your hair. 
They also last up to six months without having to maintain the extensions in between, saving you time and money, and the hair flows much more naturally, with the individual extensions rather than one big left or a few big Wefts.😉
